# bao-boss — Windsurf Rules

## Project
Bun-native PostgreSQL job queue library with SKIP LOCKED, retries, cron, pub/sub, DLQ, and HTMX dashboard.

## Stack
- Runtime: Bun (not Node.js)
- HTTP: Elysia
- ORM: Prisma 7 + PrismaPg adapter + raw SQL for SKIP LOCKED
- Dashboard: htmx (no JS frameworks)
- Validation: TypeBox (via Elysia `t`)
- Language: TypeScript strict
- Database: PostgreSQL 15+, `baoboss` schema

## Rules
- Use Bun APIs exclusively
- TypeScript strict with `noUncheckedIndexedAccess`
- ESNext modules, `.js` import extensions
- Prisma 7 for CRUD (import from `src/generated/prisma/`), raw SQL only for `FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED`
- Validate inputs with TypeBox (`t` + `Value.Decode`) in Manager.ts
- Inline HTML with htmx attributes for dashboard
- Emit errors via `boss.emit('error', err)`
- Tests: `bun test` in `packages/bao-boss/test/`

## Key Files
- `packages/bao-boss/src/BaoBoss.ts` — Main class
- `packages/bao-boss/src/Manager.ts` — Job/queue CRUD
- `packages/bao-boss/src/Worker.ts` — Polling worker
- `packages/bao-boss/src/Dashboard.ts` — htmx dashboard
- `packages/bao-boss/src/types.ts` — TypeScript types
- `packages/bao-boss/prisma/schema.prisma` — DB schema

